, Cartagena, Ciénaga Grande de Santa 
<collectingCountry box="[151,218,968,991]" name="Malta" pageId="14" pageNumber="189">Marta</collectingCountry>
and Santa 
<collectingCountry box="[341,412,968,991]" name="Malta" pageId="14" pageNumber="189">Marta</collectingCountry>
